WEBVTT

00:00:00.160 --> 00:00:08.334
Hey, good morning family! Praise the Lord. Day 53, I believe. I'm excited you're all here today.

00:00:08.335 --> 00:00:14.081
I have some things on my heart; I saw some things in the spirit yesterday that I'm going to get into.

00:00:14.082 --> 00:00:23.580
I was driving around by ORU again, and every time I drive around by ORU, there is an anointing on ORU or Oral Roberts University.

00:00:23.581 --> 00:00:35.331
I'm telling you, the grounds of Oral Roberts University—and when I drive by there, I have to go to the Post Office to deliver my stuff sometimes for my eBay.

00:00:35.332 --> 00:00:43.965
We were going to the Billy Burke meeting last night and we were so excited to go.

00:00:43.966 --> 00:00:51.828
When we showed up, the presence of the Lord was so strong on that meeting. Diana, I mean, did you feel it?

00:00:51.829 --> 00:00:58.514
"Yes, it was amazing."The glory of the Lord was there and people were getting healed of all kinds of things.

00:00:58.514 --> 00:01:05.543
Again, the power of the Lord—there's nothing like it; there's nothing like the presence of the Lord.

00:01:05.544 --> 00:01:13.822
It is beyond anything the world could ever offer. If you're strung out on drugs, there is no high like the Most High.

00:01:13.823 --> 00:01:25.280
I'm telling you, I believe a lot of people go to drugs because they're trying to find an escape from their reality, but the only escape that I've ever seen from reality is the Holy Spirit.

00:01:25.281 --> 00:01:32.590
The more you become addicted to the Holy Spirit in these last days, it's like He is the Most High, isn't it, Diana?

00:01:32.591 --> 00:01:43.121
"Yes, it's like oxygen."Exactly right. We try so hard to get in meetings like this because this is what feeds you and gets you through.

00:01:43.123 --> 00:02:01.133
When we pour out like we do on a day-to-day basis—most pastors just preach one sermon a week, maybe two—you've got to fill yourself back up.

00:02:01.134 --> 00:02:23.003
I even see myself getting dry, but in two days of being in these meetings and then going again tonight, I have an anticipation for the manifestations of the glory, seeing what He did last night again in people's lives and the night before.

00:02:23.004 --> 00:02:27.812
Sunday night, He gave us a word, prayed for us again, and the power of God was really strong.

00:02:27.813 --> 00:02:40.181
It's like the Holy Spirit is an electric charge going through you, charging your battery.

00:02:40.182 --> 00:02:46.886
You can just be sitting in the atmosphere and just drink, couldn't you, Diana?

00:02:46.887 --> 00:02:59.138
"Yes, it's amazing."I want to be someone who travels around and just goes to all the meetings. I just want to be around the presence of the Lord.

00:02:59.139 --> 00:03:15.179
I reference the anointing and the call on Billy Burke's life; I believe you honor the man of God and I honor him. Help support his ministry and go to where he's at.

00:03:15.180 --> 00:03:23.788
If he's in your area, it would behoove you to go to these meetings; the presence of the Lord will change your life.

00:03:23.789 --> 00:03:39.636
He said that the church we were visiting last night—he got in the spirit and saw the pillars and the portals.

00:03:39.637 --> 00:03:46.664
He said this place right here is one of the portals of the end times for the glory outpouring.

00:03:46.665 --> 00:04:01.226
Well, ladies and gentlemen, if you go back to what the Lord showed me about the portals coming out of the Lord's hand—I saw the great God Jehovah's hand come out of the heavens.

00:04:01.227 --> 00:04:28.097
All ten fingers had shafts of light shoot out, and I said, "Father, what is this?"and He said, "These are end-time portals for the end-time glory and the outpouring."I knew that one of them is in central Oklahoma, one is in Texas, and there's one obviously here.

00:04:28.098 --> 00:04:40.706
He said the Lord showed him that this church, Millennial Church, has an end-time portal, which I thought was amazing because he saw one of the portals.

00:04:40.707 --> 00:04:57.142
I said ten major portals went out throughout the world and then they splintered.

00:04:57.143 --> 00:05:15.239
Now, it's kind of similar to when I told you those four doves were circling and then they exploded and went to all ends of the Earth.

00:05:15.240 --> 00:05:24.262
We're seeing that, and even Billy was talking about this last outpouring; this major harvest of souls is going to start to happen.

00:05:24.263 --> 00:05:31.482
We saw a Muslim come to church last night and give his heart to Jesus Christ and he was healed.

00:05:31.483 --> 00:05:40.879
I saw the power of God knock him down on his back; he was overcoming pain in his hands and the power of the Lord healed him.

00:05:40.880 --> 00:05:54.616
With that, he accepted Jesus Christ as Lord and Savior. Folks, people are desperate, people are hungry, and they're looking for the authentic.

00:05:54.617 --> 00:06:06.810
When you taste and see that the Lord is good, there's nothing more that will satisfy that inward soul itch than the Holy Spirit.

00:06:06.811 --> 00:06:16.765
Do you agree, babe? "Yes."Diana knows; she's walked this journey with me and we know what we're talking about.

00:06:16.766 --> 00:06:24.935
We know when it's dry and when you go in and experience the presence of the Lord, it will radically change you.

00:06:24.936 --> 00:06:37.638
There's a reason why you go to service after service and you're listening to a seeker-friendly message and you're not getting changed; it's because there's no Holy Ghost there.

00:06:37.639 --> 00:07:21.638
The only way that you're going to change is by the anointing that breaks the yoke of bondage.

00:07:21.639 --> 00:07:30.215
It's the anointing that sets the captives free. But how you stay free, ladies and gentlemen, is by getting the word down inside you.

00:07:30.216 --> 00:07:39.326
The anointing can only take you so far and then you have to have the word inside of you to keep that devil at bay.

00:07:39.327 --> 00:07:44.717
Submit yourself therefore unto God, resist the devil, and he will flee from you.

00:07:44.718 --> 00:07:57.732
But the only way you submit yourself to Him is by getting that word down inside of your heart. You have to know the word and have a revelation.

00:07:57.733 --> 00:08:05.667
According to Ephesians, that the eyes of your understanding would be enlightened that you may know the hope of your calling and the glorious riches of inheritance.

00:08:05.668 --> 00:08:13.290
You have a treasure in an earthen vessel that the excellency of the power will be known of Him and not of you.

00:08:13.291 --> 00:08:30.799
The anointing breaks the yoke, but to keep the yoke off, you have to have the word of God. The enemy comes back immediately to try to test the word.

00:08:30.800 --> 00:08:43.731
If you don't have a foundation of the word of God inside of you, the anointing will break the yoke, but he automatically comes back to try to kill, steal, and destroy that revelation.

00:08:43.732 --> 00:08:56.061
The only way that you do that is by the word. The Bible says the word is a sword and it comes out of your mouth to cut the devil.

00:08:56.062 --> 00:09:42.134
You cut the devil by the word of the Lord out of your mouth, speaking out and decreeing a thing: "I am healed by the stripes of Jesus."Even Billy Burke was talking about getting that word down inside of you to resist it. Faith cometh by hearing, and hearing by the word of God.

00:09:42.135 --> 00:10:16.466
I can tell you all, literally listening to Brother Hagin all my life and other preachers—listening to them to the point where I go back and I listen to that same sermon from five years ago and get something new out of it because the word is alive.

00:10:16.467 --> 00:10:43.456
There's no expiration date on the word of God. As your spirit grows, you'll hear something new in that word because you're going from glory to glory.

00:10:43.457 --> 00:11:01.156
I've told Diana about the pillars and about the glory domes and about the outpouring of the healings coming.

00:11:01.157 --> 00:11:20.278
The Lord said, "My judgment begins in the house of the Lord first,"and we're seeing a cleaning of the house throughout all America right now, exposing darkness and turning on the light.

00:11:20.279 --> 00:11:36.888
We're going to bring in some new people to fix this room because it takes a lot of cleaning, actually.

00:11:36.889 --> 00:11:57.196
I believe 2025 is going to be an amazing year. Regardless of what we see on the news, this is your year of turnaround.

00:11:57.197 --> 00:12:07.176
This is your year for your breakthrough and to receive exceedingly abundantly above all that we dare ask or think.

00:12:07.177 --> 00:12:12.498
This is your time to lay hold of what you've been believing for.

00:12:12.499 --> 00:12:17.832
The seeds you've sowed in the past are going to come to harvest at last.

00:12:17.832 --> 00:12:23.779
I believe that this is a year of great overflow for the body of Christ.

00:12:23.780 --> 00:12:31.965
There was a dear sister in the Lord, one of the pastors from Eufaula, and she got a word about finances.

00:12:31.966 --> 00:12:38.039
The Lord spoke to them about their church in Eufaula because we visited there.

00:12:38.040 --> 00:12:53.274
We want to be like traveling word junkies. When you're desperate, people do desperate things.

00:12:53.275 --> 00:13:02.984
If you are desperate for Jesus, you won't want to stay the same anymore.

00:13:02.985 --> 00:13:14.160
You've got to get fed up with being broke, busted, and disgusted.

00:13:14.161 --> 00:13:36.393
I saw people travel from Mexico City to Oklahoma; they drove in a van because they were desperate for a touch.

00:13:36.394 --> 00:13:54.363
Then you had another man say, "I flew here from Canada."I saw two people from Canada, from British Columbia and Edmonton.

00:13:54.364 --> 00:14:11.674
Folks, that is desperate, to fly thousands of miles. How hungry are you?

00:14:11.675 --> 00:14:18.078
If he's in your area, I encourage you to go and visit because you won't leave disappointed.

00:14:18.079 --> 00:14:35.312
I want to travel to Tampa and Orlando next year. Rodney Howard-Browne has revivals.

00:14:35.312 --> 00:14:42.346
I see the tangible presence of the Lord moving in their services.

00:14:42.347 --> 00:15:10.015
Let's go and dip in the river. How thirsty are you for a supernatural touch from the Father?

00:15:10.016 --> 00:15:28.210
We're so thirsty for an authentic move of God. We're right there on the cusp.

00:15:28.211 --> 00:15:36.323
He's bringing forth the harvesters, and I believe certain investments are going to skyrocket.

00:15:36.324 --> 00:15:48.356
We're going to see a major harvest in 2025 to free us up to do the things that God's called us to do.

00:15:48.357 --> 00:16:14.757
It just takes money, and the Lord provides. When you watch these videos, I hope we encourage you to believe God for the impossible.

00:16:14.758 --> 00:16:45.994
Diana had some things she wanted to say. "People will spend a lot of money going to a spa or going on vacations for their mental health.

00:16:45.995 --> 00:17:07.594
It is important, but even more time should be spent on nourishing your spirit, like a spa for your spirit.

00:17:07.595 --> 00:17:33.516
If you're willing to invest that much time into your physical body, then how much more do we need it for our spirit man?"It's vital because you can't fight a devil weak; you have to fight from the overflow.

00:17:33.517 --> 00:18:16.158
If you're fighting on empty, you're in trouble. Fixing your spirit fixes everything from the inside out.

00:18:16.159 --> 00:18:28.319
Moses didn't fade; his eyes didn't grow dim because he stayed in the glory. The glory renews you.

00:18:28.320 --> 00:18:39.943
That's what I said before about Joe Biden and these people—when you latch on to the devil, he is a 'kill, steal, and destroy'spirit, and it makes your mind reprobate.

00:18:39.944 --> 00:18:58.603
The closer you are to the devil, the more he tears you down. That's why witches always look really old; the demonic sucks life out of you.

00:18:58.604 --> 00:19:03.873
But the Bible says that I've come that you might have life and life more abundantly.

00:19:03.874 --> 00:19:35.619
Connect yourself to the Source, and that is the glory. Moses attached himself to the glory, and their bodies weren't sick.

00:19:35.620 --> 00:19:54.152
They didn't need hair plugs or Botox; their skin looked good.

00:19:54.153 --> 00:20:18.699
The anointing is a refresher. When you go to these meetings, it refreshes you.

00:20:18.700 --> 00:20:33.849
We were sitting in the very back because we got there later back then, and we were like, "Man, Lord, we want to be on the front row,"but it doesn't matter because the Holy Spirit is tangible throughout the whole auditorium.

00:20:33.850 --> 00:20:55.798
We saw a dear sister from San Antonio; she got baptized in the Holy Ghost.

00:20:55.799 --> 00:21:21.660
She'd been a Baptist her whole life, in her 60s, and she got baptized watching one of our videos.

00:21:21.661 --> 00:21:51.432
Then I had a young man who got baptized in the Holy Ghost on this channel too. That is the first step to your victory.

00:21:51.433 --> 00:21:58.678
I don't know how anybody makes it without being baptized in the Holy Spirit, speaking with other tongues.

00:21:58.679 --> 00:22:39.086
I depend on Him; He is my all in all. I want to encourage you all to get filled.

00:22:39.087 --> 00:22:56.072
Get the book 'Why Tongues'by Brother Hagin. It's Kenneth E. Hagin. Read that book over and over again.

00:22:56.073 --> 00:23:08.973
I didn't even get into what I saw in the spirit about Donald Jr., but we'll make another video tomorrow.

00:23:08.974 --> 00:23:30.599
Let's pray. Father, we thank You for every person here today.

00:23:30.600 --> 00:23:52.282
We thank You that You're filling them to the overflow right now in the name of Jesus.

00:23:52.283 --> 00:24:29.687
They are filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit. I believe for demonstrations of the glory on people's lives today.

00:24:29.688 --> 00:24:52.839
We reach out for your healing and deliverance. We are joint heirs with Jesus Christ, seated in the heavenlies far above all principalities.

00:24:52.840 --> 00:25:18.066
Diana, pray for the women. "Yes, Father, I lift up these women that have any hormonal imbalances.

00:25:18.067 --> 00:25:33.723
I thank You that everything lines up with Your word. Our hormones line up in the name of Jesus.

00:25:33.724 --> 00:26:16.094
Cycles are regulated, and the reproductive system works as it should. We speak to our bodies.

00:26:16.095 --> 00:26:27.262
If you're believing for a baby, you say, 'Womb, you line up with the word of God; you will conceive.'Speak to those body parts."I agree.

00:26:27.263 --> 00:27:07.481
I feel the anointing. "Hormones, you line up with the word of God. Every cell in my body functions as my Creator designed it.

00:27:07.482 --> 00:28:05.032
Father, if it's your foot, say, 'Foot, line up with the word of God; pain, go now.'Bones straightened, thyroid function, gallbladders, and bile ducts—function like the Lord designed us to, in Jesus'name."I can have everything the Bible says I can have.

00:28:05.033 --> 00:28:45.501
Amen. "People have been coming up to me telling me they conceived because they prayed with me on video.

00:28:45.502 --> 00:29:09.569
Lots of babies are coming in 2025."We're humbled to be used.

00:29:09.570 --> 00:30:09.661
Whoever thought it would be through a YouTube channel? We've come across such nice folks like Robert and Kay.

00:30:09.662 --> 00:30:37.582
We pray for your financial breakthroughs. We're believing for Elon Musk to become radically born again in 2025 and use Starlink for the glory of God.

00:30:37.582 --> 00:31:05.965
We call the celebrities filled with the Holy Spirit. We thank You, Lord, that Donald Trump is radically born again and his marriage is restored.

00:31:05.966 --> 00:31:36.660
We thank You for supernatural covering over his children. Father, we give You glory.

00:31:36.661 --> 00:32:10.677
There's a turning of the tides. Everybody say amen. Thank you for joining.

00:32:10.678 --> 00:32:44.518
Please like, subscribe, and click the notification bell. Put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:32:44.519 --> 00:32:56.948
Jesus loves you, and we love you. We will see you next time. God bless you.

